## 1. 下载并安装录制程序

### Linux

To install/update ascii.io recorder, open a terminal and run following
command:

我们制作了2个工具;1个录播,1个直播。2个工具可以独立使用。

安装录播工具：

    $ curl  http://www.codepark.us/asciiio >asciiio 
    $ chmod +x asciiio

asciiio 是一个python程序,需要python alsa(录音),gtk(截屏)等库。

    $ sudo aptitude install python-alsaaudio
    $ sudo aptitude install python-gtk2
    $ sudo aptitude install python-xlib
    $ sudo aptitude install lame 
    $ sudo easy_install wave

也可以使用 easy_install 安装

安装直播工具：

     直播工具是基于录播工具修改而来，需要增加python的websocket库。

     $ curl http://www.codepark.us/codepark_liveroom >codepark_liveroom
     $ chmod  + x codepark_liveroom

websocket库的安装。

     $ sudo easy_install websocket   


### OSX (暂时不提供录音和截屏功能)



If you don't use Homebrew then install/update with:

    $ curl -sL www.codepark.us/asciiio | bash

## 2. 录播使用方法

Open our terminal and run following command:

    $ ./asciiio


## 3. 直播使用方法

    $ ./codepark_liveroom n

n 为房间号码。

codepark_liveroom 直播结束后也可以上传到网站。


New shell instance will be opened and everything you'll do in it will be
recorded. When you're ready to upload simply exit the shell with `exit`
command or just hit `<C-d>`.

## 3. Create profile (optional)

If you want your recordings to be assigned to your ascii.io profile and to be
able to edit/delete them run this and follow instructions:

    $ asciiio auth

If you skip this step now, you can always run above command later and all
previously recorded asciicasts will get automatically assigned to your new
profile.

